would take the presidency a decision he will likely have to make 
within the next week 
i havent gone to confession in a very long time and i can see 
that you want me to confess joked the communist who grew up in a 
roman catholic family but i used to go i used to go 
he said his candidacy would depend on democratic 
consultations within the party and could not be decided by him alone 
